{"name": "ShuffleResult", "xref": {"fqname": "pathvein.lib.ShuffleResult", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Recursively scan a source path for pattern-spec directory structures and copy them to their destination\n\nShuffleInput.source will be copied to ShuffleInput.destination, not _into_ it.\nThe direct children of ShuffleInput.source will be direct children of ShuffleInput.destination"]}, {"name": "pathvein.lib.shuffle_to", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "matches", "type": {"name": "Set", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Set", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "ScanResult", "xref": {"fqname": "pathvein.lib.ScanResult", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "destination", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "overwrite", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "dryrun", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "ShuffleResult", "xref": {"fqname": "pathvein.lib.ShuffleResult", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Recursively scan a source path for pattern-spec directory structures and copy them into a single destination_fn\n\nEach match will be copied into a flat structure at `destination / match.source.name`"]}, {"name": "pathvein.lib.shuffle_with", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "matches", "type": {"name": "Set", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Set", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "ScanResult", "xref": {"fqname": "pathvein.lib.ScanResult", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "destination_fn", "type": {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "", "xref": null, "params": [{"name": "ScanResult", "xref": {"fqname": "pathvein.lib.ScanResult", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "overwrite", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "dryrun", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "ShuffleResult", "xref": {"fqname": "pathvein.lib.ShuffleResult", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Recursively scan a source path for pattern-spec directory structures and copy them to the destination_fn\n\nProvide a function that takes a ScanResult and returns a destination Path for that result. This allows for\nexpressive control over the destination of each match."]}], "variables": [{"name": "pathvein.lib.logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "pathvein.lib.ScanResult", "bases": ["NamedTuple"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "pathvein.lib.ScanResult.source", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pathvein.lib.ScanResult.pattern", "type": {"name": "FileStructurePattern", "xref": {"fqname": "pathvein.lib.pattern.FileStructurePattern", "project": null}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["In order to support back to python 3.8 we need to declare these as NamedTuple subclasses", "instead of using the new-type style definition with \"ScanResult = NamedTuple(...)\" format."]}, {"name": "pathvein.lib.ShuffleInput", "bases": ["NamedTuple"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "pathvein.lib.Shuf